31:00.108 --> 31:02.276
Aah! Aah!
Is it me? Oh, G...

31:03.111 --> 31:05.821
Probably a good idea
to have a fire
extinguisher around.

31:05.906 --> 31:07.114
You think?
Mmm.

31:12.955 --> 31:14.038
STEVE: Ah, no.

31:15.916 --> 31:17.458
More lights? No.

31:22.172 --> 31:24.173
Buddy! Buddy?

31:25.092 --> 31:26.133
Hey, what are you doing?

31:26.301 --> 31:27.385
Hi, Steve.

31:27.469 --> 31:28.844
Getting more lights?

31:28.971 --> 31:30.388
Yeah. Is that your
shop across the street?

31:30.472 --> 31:31.973
This is wrong.
All this has to go back.

31:32.099 --> 31:33.558
Just the man
I needed to see.

31:33.642 --> 31:35.601
What do you think of the tree
for Winterfest?

31:35.686 --> 31:37.436
Well...
Actually, Steve,

31:37.521 --> 31:41.107
I was talking to Buddy here.
After all, he is the expert.

31:42.192 --> 31:43.442
Come on.
Would you have a look?

31:44.278 --> 31:46.487
Watch my stuff, Steve.
Now...

31:47.322 --> 31:48.781
Folks,
everything's free today.

31:48.865 --> 31:49.991
Anything you want.
It's all free.

31:50.075 --> 31:53.452
BUDDY: I love the colored
strands of lights.
The spacing is great.

31:53.829 --> 31:54.829
Thank you.

31:54.913 --> 31:55.955
The ornaments
well dispersed.

31:56.498 --> 31:57.832
Oh, yes.

31:58.166 --> 32:02.003
I see you're using
my bulb of choice, the C-9.
(CHUCKLING)

32:02.921 --> 32:07.008
Very nice!
That adds a lot of class
to that tree. I love it.

32:07.509 --> 32:08.801
(LAUGHS) Thank you!
Really good.

32:09.136 --> 32:10.928
He likes it!
Hey, Steve.

32:11.054 --> 32:13.764
That...
That is a tree.
Yes, it is.

32:13.849 --> 32:14.974
Huh?
Yeah.

32:15.058 --> 32:17.810
Listen, we need
to get something straight.

32:17.894 --> 32:20.521
Around here
I'm the Christmas guy.

32:20.939 --> 32:22.273
Really?
Yeah. Yeah.

32:22.357 --> 32:23.858
It's kinda my thing.

32:24.985 --> 32:26.944
Uh, Chris has
Memorial Day,

32:27.029 --> 32:29.780
Pete has the Fourth of July,
but I have Christmas.

32:29.865 --> 32:31.073
Oh.

32:31.199 --> 32:32.408
But, hey,
hey, you can
have Halloween.

32:32.492 --> 32:33.868
Yeah. Yeah,
good. Halloween.

32:33.994 --> 32:35.328
Yeah, sure, sure.

32:35.412 --> 32:37.788
Couple of pumpkins in
the yard, a skeleton or two,

32:37.873 --> 32:39.332
you can jump out
and scare people.

32:39.374 --> 32:41.334
It'll be great.
What do you think?
I don't think so.

32:41.585 --> 32:42.627
No?

32:42.753 --> 32:43.794
This Winterfest thing...

32:43.879 --> 32:45.087
What is this all about?

32:45.172 --> 32:47.673
Oh, it's our...
Our annual
Christmas carnival.

32:47.758 --> 32:48.841
Wow.

32:48.967 --> 32:50.051
Yeah, we have
a show, games,

32:50.135 --> 32:51.802
ice sculpture, races.

32:51.887 --> 32:53.220
I happen to be
the chairman.

32:53.263 --> 32:55.473
