make me an offer?

37:45.555 --> 37:46.931
No. I need to get out.

37:48.350 --> 37:49.725
Okay.

37:49.809 --> 37:51.393
Scoot on through.

37:52.437 --> 37:53.437
I don't know.

37:53.521 --> 37:56.190
I swear to God,
men can't drive anymore.

37:56.274 --> 37:57.858
You hold my beer,
I'll do it for you.

37:57.984 --> 37:59.568
Okay, okay, I'll do it.

37:59.653 --> 38:01.654
Just...
Just guide me out.

38:03.073 --> 38:04.365
All right.

38:06.993 --> 38:08.535
Hey, you could
probably use a few more

38:08.662 --> 38:10.204
