Look at that thing!

38:12.207 --> 38:13.207
All right, you ready?

38:13.333 --> 38:14.375
You sure?

38:14.793 --> 38:19.213
That's why I'm here,
buddy. Don't worry.
I'm watchin' ya. I'm watchin'.

38:19.673 --> 38:23.592
A little bit to your right.
No, no, your other right!
Yeah! Come on!

38:23.677 --> 38:25.678
