the other side at all.

38:25.804 --> 38:27.805
That's okay. I'm your eyes.

38:27.889 --> 38:29.390
I'm your eyes.

38:30.976 --> 38:32.851
Straight back.
Doesn't look like
enough room to me.

38:39.776 --> 38:41.235
Oh! Oh, boy!
(CRIES OUT)

38:50.870 --> 38:52.329
Oh, that's ugly.

38:52.580 --> 38:54.248
Okay. Okay.
It's all right!

38:54.708 --> 38:57.084
At this point, it's like
pulling off a Band-Aid.

38:57.210 --> 38:59.586
You gotta just gun it!
You know?

38:59.671 --> 39:01.588
Okay. You ready?

39:01.881 --> 39:04.049
One, two...

39:04.426 --> 39:05.843
Gun it!

