Please. Oh, come on!

39:27.115 --> 39:28.657
(POP CHRISTMAS MUSIC PLAYING)

39:48.720 --> 39:51.388
Sheriff Dave,
you have to do something
about my neighbor's house.

39:51.473 --> 39:53.223
Oh, yeah, yeah,
the Hall place.

39:53.308 --> 39:55.726
I take my kids by there
every night after dinner.
(LAUGHS)

39:55.810 --> 39:57.561
It just keeps
gettin' bigger and bigger.

39:57.645 --> 40:01.523
Yes, well, that's...
That's why I want
you to arrest him.

40:01.608 --> 40:03.150
Arrest him?
On what charge?

40:03.318 --> 40:04.902
Light trespass.

40:04.986 --> 40:06.653
Light trespass?
Uh-huh.

40:07.489 --> 40:09.615
Yes. Light trespass.

40:10.075 --> 40:11.909
"When bright,
uncontrolled light

40:11.993 --> 40:14.453
"shines in neighboring
property or windows

40:14.537 --> 40:17.081
"as to cause
a public nuisance."

40:17.165 --> 40:20.000
Well, I'm...
I'm public, and I've been

40:20.502 --> 40:21.585
nuisanced.

40:21.669 --> 40:25.255
I can't arrest
a man for dÃ©cor...
What are you looking at?

40:25.965 --> 40:27.591
What, this?
No! No.

40:27.675 --> 40:30.594
I... I don't mind
if you wear a br...

40:31.012 --> 40:32.971
I... Looks like
a nice one.

40:33.515 --> 40:36.433
It's a brace.
My wife made it for me.

40:36.518 --> 40:38.894
I dislocated my shoulder.
It keeps it from
popping back out.

40:38.978 --> 40:39.937
Sure.

40:40.021 --> 40:41.063
What'd you think?

40:41.147 --> 40:42.564
(LAUGHS)

40:42.857 --> 40:44.483
Did you think I
was wearing a bra?

40:44.567 --> 40:48.487
No, no. That would...
That would be crazy.
(CHUCKLES)

40:49.155 --> 40:51.782
Now, as far as
the lights are concerned,

40:51.908 --> 40:53.742
I'm saying
it's Christmas...
Mm-hmm.

40:53.827 --> 40:54.952
...and you've got
a lot on your mind,

40:55.078 --> 40:56.203
what with
the Winterfest coming up.

40:56.287 --> 40:59.790
But if you want to
file a complaint,
I'll fill out the paperwork.

40:59.874 --> 41:02.709
I do.
Thank you. I appreciate it.
I want to file a complaint.

41:03.336 --> 41:04.461
Now,

41:05.380 --> 41:07.381
where is that form?

41:08.633 --> 41:10.759
Yes. Here we are.

41:14.389 --> 41:15.639
Dr. Finch?

41:19.227 --> 41:20.227
Yo.

41:21.271 --> 41:22.646
