41:23.106 --> 41:25.816
What happened?
I woke up, and you were gone.

41:25.900 --> 41:27.651
What are you
doing out here?

41:27.735 --> 41:28.735
(GASPS)

41:29.237 --> 41:30.404
Honey!

41:31.072 --> 41:33.282
You've really been doing
a lot of work.

41:33.366 --> 41:34.366
Yeah.

41:34.450 --> 41:35.617
It looks amazing.

41:38.454 --> 41:39.454
(SIGHS)

41:40.665 --> 41:43.500
I guess the light thing
is pretty stupid, isn't it?

41:43.585 --> 41:45.169
Oh, honey.

41:47.505 --> 41:49.173
Yeah, it is.

41:50.675 --> 41:53.343
Oh, come on.
It's the stupidest
thing I've ever heard.

41:53.428 --> 41:55.679
