of my special holiday offers,

42:07.150 --> 42:08.984
I think you know
what I mean.

42:09.068 --> 42:10.152
You just said
they look stupid.

42:10.278 --> 42:11.403
Yeah! It's crazy!

42:11.863 --> 42:14.031
But all good ideas
are crazy.

42:15.283 --> 42:16.450
These are lights.

42:16.868 --> 42:18.243
Oh, come on.

42:19.412 --> 42:23.123
I think we both know
it means more to
you than just lights.

42:26.794 --> 42:28.128
Who knows?

42:28.963 --> 42:30.672
Might turn out to be

42:32.967 --> 42:34.760
something monumental.

42:40.225 --> 42:41.600
I can always count
on you, can't I?

42:41.726 --> 42:43.143
Sure.

42:45.480 --> 42:46.480
Mmm.

42:49.108 --> 42:51.693
Oh, cow!
We'll have
buttermilk pancakes tomorrow.

42:52.028 --> 42:53.695
What is he up to now?

42:53.780 --> 42:56.031
