for a live manger scene.

42:56.115 --> 42:57.157
Unbelievable.

42:57.784 --> 42:58.867
STEVE: Is that a camel?

42:58.952 --> 43:00.202
BUDDY: Look at that.

43:00.328 --> 43:01.620
DELIVERYMAN: Yep.

43:02.163 --> 43:03.997
Can't wait to
run my kids by.

43:04.082 --> 43:05.332
Well, if you wanna
make sure they see it,

43:05.500 --> 43:06.750
you'd better
bring 'em tonight.

